      </p>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-3">
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            What is Endfield Factory Planner?
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light group-open:hidden">+</span>
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light hidden group-open:inline">−</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5"><p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">It's a free web-based tool that calculates optimal factory layouts for Arknights: Endfield. You select a target item, specify your desired production rate, and it shows you the complete recipe tree, required buildings, and how to connect them.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            How accurate are the calculations?
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light group-open:hidden">+</span>
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light hidden group-open:inline">−</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5"><p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">All recipes and production times are sourced directly from the game data. The calculator computes exact ratios to ensure 100% efficiency with zero idle time. Building counts are rounded up to give you the minimum whole buildings needed.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            Is this similar to Factorio's production planner?
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light group-open:hidden">+</span>
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light hidden group-open:inline">−</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5"><p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes! Arknights: Endfield shares many factory mechanics with Factorio. If you've used tools like Factorio Calculator or Kirk McDonald's planner, you'll feel right at home. We've adapted the concept specifically for Endfield's recipe chains.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            What buildings are supported?
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light group-open:hidden">+</span>
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light hidden group-open:inline">−</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5"><p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">We support all 7 production building types: Greenhouse, Grinder, Smelter, Workshop, Mixer, Assembler, and Chemical Lab. Each building has its own production speed and recipe set built into our database.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            Will you update recipes for new game patches?
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light group-open:hidden">+</span>
            <span class="text-accent text-xl font-light hidden group-open:inline">−</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-5"><p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Absolutely. Our game data specialist monitors every patch and beta update. Recipe changes are typically reflected in our database within 24 hours of a new game version release.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden group open:border-accent transition-colors">
          <summary class="px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer font-semibold text-base text-text-primary flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-card-hover transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
